      "author": "lumargh",
      "description": "## Calendar List 1.1.0\n\n### Settings\n- New **List format** group for the prefix and title separator.\n- New **Output preview** that renders a live sample list reflecting all your format settings.\n- Format previews now appear **below** their inputs, with clearer spacing between the date and time options.\n- Date-related inputs are **disabled when “Include date” is off**; time format and the date–time separator are disabled when “Include time” is off.\n- New **Include time** toggle (default on).\n- New **First day of week** setting that controls the “This week” / “Next week” ranges.\n- New installs now default to the **ISO date format** (`YYYY-MM-DD`).\n\n### Ranges & events\n- Fixed an off-by-one so fetches **include the end date**.\n- “This week” / “Next week” now respect your chosen first day of the week.\n- **Multi-day events** are shown as a `start – end` span instead of a single (often out-of-range) start date.\n\n### Editor & modal\n- The **Custom…** range option can now be chosen via the keyboard.\n- Typing in the custom date fields no longer triggers a preset or an early insert.\n- The cursor now lands at the **end** of an inline-inserted list.",
